    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……どれにしよう……\n困ったなぁ……",
      "startTime": 3.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2233.3333333000005,
          "startTime": 5.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　葵さん、何を書いて……あ、それ『ミラクル\n☆アイドルバースデー！』のアンケートじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 12.3999999682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルがしたいことを叶えてくれる、雑誌のお誕生日\n企画ですよね。ついに葵さんの番が来たんですね～！",
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね。でも、何を書こうか悩んでるんだ\nこころに相談して、アイデアは沢山出たんだけどね",
      "startTime": 27.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、「莉央にバンジージャンプをしてほしい」とか\n「莉央にぬるぬるの床の上でお相撲をしてほしい」とか",
      "startTime": 36.0000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "なんで莉央さんに体を張らせようとするんですか！？\nせっかくのお誕生日がギャグになっちゃいますよ！",
      "startTime": 43.2000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、莉央のそんな面白……\n体を張った気高い姿が見られるのは今回くらいだよ",
      "startTime": 50.5000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_51_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、撮影当日に向けて練習する莉央と愛の姿を\nこころと二人で密着取材するつもりだよ",
      "startTime": 59.6000026703,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}